    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UNITED\nAIR LINES\nMENU\nTHANKSGIVING DINNER ALOFT\nFresh Cider Cocktail Hearts of Celery\nRoast Northwestern Turkey\nwith Chestnut Stuffing and Cranberry Sauce\nGlazed Sweet Potatoes\nBrussels Sprouts\nDinner Rolls\nAssorted Breads\nMainliner Salad, Puritan\nPumpkin Pie\nRoasted Nuts Cluster Raisins\nMints\nCoffee\nTea\nCigarettes\nChocolate\nNovember 24, 25, 26, 1937\nIt is our pleasure to serve you\nthis meal with our compliments.\nDonald Magarrell Maitre d'Airline",
